node.text:
To celebrate international yoga day, we invited our IIN ambassador @withyohanna to hold an online yoga class for you. 🧘‍♀️ 

Yohanna is a yoga teacher and wellness coach based in Stockholm, Sweden. After healing from burnout and eating disorder, she now guides ambitious women to balanced and meaningful lives through coaching, events and retreats. 🙏🏻

Yohanna happily shares her experience of being a student of IIN and welcome you to reach out via IG to ask questions. Remember to mention “Yohanna Mannelqvist” when you book your program to receive her ambassador discount of $2000! 💕🙌🏼

node.text:
We got kicked out at the end of our yin yoga stretch, but had a great conversation about the importance of breathwork & stretching to overall mental & physical wellness. 

We also discussed my experience with IIN, what led me to the program & how it’s shaped my life, health & career. 

You can follow me @coachcalie to continue the discussion. And don’t miss out on the opportunity yet the IIN sample class linked in my Instagram profile.

node.text:
Change is a process, not an event. Congratulations @nataliemacielsch!

I experimented with my body, mind and spirit. I now know what nurtures me and keeps me on the path to continue learning.

I am here to help and support everyone in the personal transformation process to achieve well-being, improve the quality of life, taking into account health in a holistic way and the concept of bio individuality.

This is just the beginning!

“Experimenté con mi cuerpo, mente y espíritu. Gracias a eso hoy puedo conocerlo mejor, saber lo que me nutre, dejar de lado la comparación y escucharlo, seguir aprendiendo.

Escuchar las necesidades de nuestro ser es fundamental para encontrar nuestro propio equilibrio.

Especialmente comprender que cada unx es un ser individual y qué hay caminos diferentes para lograr el bienestar.

Estoy para ayudarlos y apoyarlos en el proceso de transformación personal para lograr el bienestar, mejorar la calidad de vida, teniendo en cuenta a la salud de manera holística y por sobretodo transmitirles el concepto de la bioinvidualidad.”

IIN Holistic Health Coach @nutritionschool

#iinhealthcoach #iinalumni #selflove #holistichealth #coaching #argentina #bariloche #bioindividuality

node.text: Kale is still king with it’s antioxidant, immunity and vitamin rich powers. It’s an excellent source of calcium, iron, vitamin A and C, and chlorophyll. But you already know that all, share what you love about kale in comments. #primaryfood #nutritionschool 🥬

node.text: “If you do just one thing to live a healthier life, focus on your sleep! A proper night’s sleep helps our bodies repair and reset, and getting a poor night’s sleep for just one night can wreak havoc on our blood sugar and mood.” Wise words from IIN CEO @lynda.cloud and inspiration from IIN health coach,  @nutritionrefresh

“In 2015 I proudly received my certification as an Integrative Nutrition Health Coach (INHC), and have been implementing my coaching to women world-wide ever since. This has been 6+ years in the making ✨

3 Things I've learned along the way:

1. Our health is so much more than the food we eat and the exercise we do

2. We are all bio-individuals: no two people are meant to eat, move or live the same

3. Given half the chance, the body can heal itself with proper custom nutrients and care. Drugs or medications are not needed. 

🌸I challenge you to let go of what is not adding value or purpose to your life, and finally take control 🌸” - IIN Health Coach @alannatasios
